snippet.title: LEO - Naa Ready Lyric Video | Thalapathy Vijay | Lokesh Kanagaraj | Anirudh Ravichander
snippet.description:
In the smashing vocals of #ThalapathyVijay here comes the most -awaited #Leo first single #NaaReady composed by Rockstar Anirudh ! Directed by Lokesh Kanagaraj this one is sure to top charts and hearts alike!

Song Title : Naa Ready
Album / Movie : Leo
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Vocals - Thalapathy Vijay & Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Vishnu Edavan
Rap written & performed by Asal Kolaar 

Starring - Thalapathy Vijay, Sanjay Dutt, Trisha, Arjun, Gautham Vasudev Menon, Mysskin, Mansoor Ali Khan, Priya Anand

Written & Directed by Lokesh Kanagaraj
Music : Anirudh Ravichander
Producer : Lalit Kumar
Co Producer : Jagadish Palanisamy
Banner : Seven Screen Studio
Director of Photography : Manoj Paramahamsa
Action : Anbariv 
Editor : Philomin Raj 
Art Direction : N. Sathees Kumar 
Choreography : Dinesh
Costume designers - Pallavi Singh, Eka Lakhani, Praveen Raja
Dialogue Writer : Lokesh Kanagaraj, Rathna Kumar, Deeraj Vaidy
PRO :  Riaz K Ahmed  
Publicity Designer : Gopi Prasannaa
Sound Designer : SYNC Cinema 
Sound Mixing : Kannan Ganapat 
Production Controller : KTS Swaminathan
Executive Producer : Ramkumar Balasubramanian
Associate Director : Santhosh Krishnan, Sathya, Immanuel Prakash, Rohith Surya
Colorist : Glen Castinho   Assistant Colorist : Nesikaa Rajakumaran
DI : Igene

Keyboard, Synth & Rhythm Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander

Additional Keyboard Programmed by OfRo, Arish & Pradeep PJ
Music Advisor - Ananthakrrishnan
Creative Consultant - Sajith Satya

snippet.title: Living like a Mermaid 🧜‍♀️ for a day!
snippet.description:
🧜‍♀️ Living Like a Mermaid for a Day! 🌊 Dive into an enchanting underwater adventure as we take on the ultimate mermaid challenge. Join us on this magical journey as we transform into mermaids and explore the wonders of the ocean! 🐠

In this captivating vlog, we'll show you how we prepared for our day as mermaids, including getting our mermaid tails, creating mesmerizing mermaid makeup looks, and styling our hair with shimmering shells and pearls. 🧜‍♀️✨

Once we're fully transformed, we'll take you along as we dive into the crystal-clear waters, swimming gracefully like real mermaids. Get ready to witness stunning underwater footage as we encounter colorful marine life, mystical coral reefs, and maybe even discover hidden treasures! 🐚🌈

But being a mermaid isn't just about swimming. We'll also indulge in delightful mermaid-themed snacks and drinks, perfecting our mermaid poses and dances, and enjoying the magical serenity of the ocean's embrace. It's a day filled with joy, wonder, and a touch of mermaid magic! 🌊🎉

So, if you've ever wondered what it's like to live as a mermaid, or simply want to embark on a whimsical adventure with us, don't miss this extraordinary experience. Dive into the deep blue with us and let your imagination swim free in this unforgettable mermaid journey! 🧜‍♀️💙

Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe to our channel to stay tuned for more incredible adventures. Hit that notification bell so you never miss a moment of our magical escapades! 🔔✨

Aayiye dekhte hai ki Damad ji ke nakhro ko kaise sambhala Vikas aur uski Platina 110 ABS ne jo hai poore duniya ki sabse surakshit 110cc bike hai. Iska ABS on toh phisalna off!

#TVF #GajjabBejjatiHai #AasifKhan

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel:

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 55 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 21st June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 56 Teaser - 21st June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 56 Teaser - 21st June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

#yumnazaidi

snippet.title: Biparjoy का Rajasthan में असर Barmer में बारिश ने 25 साल का रिकॉर्ड तोड़ा, कई इलाकों में बाढ़
snippet.description:
#biparjoy #rajasthanweather #heavyrain #amarujalanews 
चक्रवाती तूफान बिपरजॉय अब राजस्थान में कहर मचा रहा है। प्रदेश के कई जिलों में बीते 24 घंटे से लगातार हो रही बारिश हो रही है साथ ही तेज हवा भी चल रही है, जिससे जनजीवन अस्त-व्यस्त हो गया है। बाड़मेर में बाढ़ जैसे हालात हैं.

Biparjoy का Rajasthan में असर Barmer में बारिश ने 25 साल का रिकॉर्ड तोड़ा, कई इलाकों में बाढ़

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 57 Teaser - 22nd June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 57 Teaser - 22nd June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

Mastaney's Teaser Starring TARSEM JASSAR, SIMI CHAHAL, GURPREET GHUGGI, KARAMJIT ANMOL, HONEY MATTU, BANINDER BUNNY, RAHUL DEV, AVTAR GILL, ARIF ZAKARIA & OTHERS

Producer - AASHU MUNISH SAHNI, KARAMJIT SINGH JOHAL, RAJVINDER SINGH DHILLON

Narration:-

Jab jab jurm nagade waaje 
Tab tab soore ran me gaaje 

Nadar chad ke hind pe aaea 
Singhan akaal akaal bulayea 

Khoti agar hakumat aave 
Dehi  ke fir daam lagave 

Jab nakli tu asal banave

snippet.title: നിങ്ങൾക്ക് അറിയാത്ത നീതുസിന്റെ  ജീവിതം | @Neethuzzz | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
തന്മയത്വമുള്ള അഭിനയവും കണ്ടന്റും കൊണ്ട് യുട്യൂബിൽ അഞ്ചര ലക്ഷം ആരാധകരെ സ്വന്തമാക്കാന്‍ ഈ വൈറൽ വീട്ടമ്മയ്ക്ക് സാധിച്ചു. ടിക് ടോകിലൂടെ തുടങ്ങിയ അഭിനയമാണ് നീതുവിനെ ഇന്ന് മറ്റാരുടെയും മുന്നിൽ കൈനീട്ടാതെ സ്വന്തമായി സമ്പാദിക്കാൻ കഴിയുന്ന നിലയിൽ കൊണ്ടെത്തിച്ചത്. നമ്മളെ ഒക്കെ ചിരിപ്പിച്ചു സന്തോഷിപ്പിക്കുന്ന നീതുവിനും പറയാനുണ്ട് കൊറേ വേദനപ്പിക്കുന്ന അനുഭവങ്ങൾ . Tiktok ലൂടെയാണ് നീതു ആദ്യമായി വീഡിയോസ് ചെയ്യാൻ തുടങ്ങിയത്. പിന്നീട് youtube ലും instagram ലും വീഡിയോസ് ചെയ്യതാണ് നീതു താരം അവൻ തുടങ്ങിയത്.  തന്റെ കുട്ടികാലത്തും പിന്നീടും അനുഭവിച്ച വെല്ലുവിളികളും ആണ് നീതു ഇന്നത്തെ വിഡിയോയിൽ പങ്കുവെക്കുന്നത് .

With her exceptional acting skills and captivating personality, Neethu gained a dedicated fan base of over five lakh on YouTube. Her viral videos brought her recognition and allowed her to make a name for herself without relying on others. She has shared both joyful and painful experiences that resonate with all of us. It all started with her videos on TikTok, and later she expanded to YouTube and Instagram. In her current video, she reflects on the challenges she faced in her childhood and throughout her journey.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.
If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalees. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

#joshtalksmalayalam #motivation  #nevergiveup

Tiktok ലൂടെയാണ് നീതു ആദ്യമായി വീഡിയോസ് ചെയ്യാൻ തുടങ്ങിയത്. പിന്നീട് youtube ലും instagram ലും വീഡിയോസ് ചെയ്യതാണ് നീതു താരം അവൻ തുടങ്ങിയത്.  തന്റെ കുട്ടികാലത്തും പിന്നീടും അനുഭവിച്ച വെല്ലുവിളികളും ആണ് നീതു ഇന്നത്തെ വിഡിയോയിൽ പങ്കുവെക്കുന്നത് .

With her exceptional acting skills and captivating personality, Neethu gained a dedicated fan base of over five lakh on YouTube. Her viral videos brought her recognition and allowed her to make a name for herself without relying on others. She has shared both joyful and painful experiences that resonate with all of us. It all started with her videos on TikTok, and later she expanded to YouTube and Instagram. In her current video, she reflects on the challenges she faced in her childhood and throughout her journey.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.
If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalees. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

🏖𝐒𝐮𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐫 धमाका ऑफ़र (𝟐𝟏 से 𝟐𝟑 जून)🔥
उत्कर्ष एप के सभी ऑनलाइन कोर्सेस पर शानदार डिस्काउंट!🤩 साथ ही कोई भी 𝐋𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐅𝐫𝐨𝐦 𝐂𝐥𝐚𝐬𝐬𝐫𝐨𝐨𝐦 कोर्स लेने पर 𝐍𝐂𝐄𝐑𝐓 𝐅𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐎𝐧𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐞 कोर्स 𝐅𝐑𝐄𝐄 🤩🥳
🛑उत्कर्ष एप पर 📚𝐁𝐨𝐨𝐤शाला से अब घर बैठे 𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐝 𝐍𝐨𝐭𝐞𝐬, 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐚𝐳𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬 व 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐲 𝐌𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐥 मगाएँ और पाएँ 𝟔𝟎% तक का 𝐎𝐅𝐅! तो आज ही 𝐃𝐨𝐰𝐧𝐥𝐨𝐚𝐝 करें 𝐔𝐭𝐤𝐚𝐫𝐬𝐡 𝐀𝐩𝐩 और शुरू करें जीत की शानदार तैयारी !!
📌https://bit.ly/UtkarshClasses_YT

snippet.title: Challengers - Official Trailer - Warner Bros. UK & Ireland
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for #ChallengersMovie starring Zendaya, Josh O’Connor, and Mike Faist. Directed by Luca Guadagnino, only in cinemas September 15.

From visionary filmmaker Luca Guadagnino, Challengers stars Zendaya as Tashi Duncan, a former tennis prodigy turned coach and a force of nature who makes no apologies for her game on and off the court. Married to a champion on a losing streak (Mike Faist – West Side Story), Tashi’s strategy for her husband’s redemption takes a surprising turn when he must face off against the washed-up Patrick (Josh O’Connor – The Crown) – his former best friend and Tashi’s former boyfriend. As their pasts and presents collide, and tensions run high, Tashi must ask herself, what will it cost to win.

snippet.title: उस लड़की को बोल चुके थे IAS बनकर दिखाएंगे | Aaditya Pandey | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Aaditya Pandey has brought AIR-48 to the UPSC examination 2023 and will become IAS. Once people used to tell their father that their son will not be able to do anything. Then somehow he did engineering and then did MBA. Then he had a breakup, after which he decided that he would crack UPSC. After working hard for 3 years and failing twice in UPSC, he cracked UPSC and got AIR-48. During the UPSC interview, many people told him that he spoke too much and needs to be toned down, but he cracked the UPSC interview with full confidence.

Today Aaditya Pandey will tell his UPSC success story through Josh Talks. So do watch this Hindi Motivational/Inspirational video of Josh Talks completely.

Aaditya Pandey जी UPSC examination 2023 में AIR-48 लेकर आए हैं और IAS बनने जा रहे हैं. एक वक्त लोग इनके पिता को कहते थे की आपका बेटा कुछ नहीं कर पाएगा. फिर इन्होंने जैसे तैसे Engineering करी फिर MBA करी. फिर इनका एक Breakup हुआ जिसके बाद इन्होंने तय किया की ये IAS बनकर रहेंगे. 3 साल तक लगातार मेहनत और UPSC में 2 बार fail होने के बाद इन्होंने UPSC Crack किया और AIR-48 हासिल की. UPSC interview के दौरान इन्हें बहुत सारे लोगों ने बोल की ये ज़्यादा बोलते है इन्हें Toned down करने की जरूरत है लेकिन इन्होंने पूरे Confidance के साथ UPSC interview crack किया. 

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Aaditya Pandey जी सुनाएंगे अपनी UPSC की success story. तो जोश Talks की इस Hindi Motivational/Inspirational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें. 

#JoshTalksHindi #AdityaPandeyJoshTalks #UPSCMotivation #UPSCSuccessStory

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi... 

DISCLAIMER -
All of the views and work outside the pretext of the video of the speaker, are his/ her own, and Josh Talks, by any means, does not support them directly or indirectly and neither is it liable for it. Viewers are requested to use their own discretion while viewing the content and focus on the entirety of the story rather than finding inferences in its parts. Josh Talks by any means, does not further or amplify any specific ideology or propaganda.

वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3803: Boss Ki Permission
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak ultimately chooses to follow Bagha's advice and speak with his supervisor before leaving about his legal issues. While he is at his boss's cabin, Taarak instructs Bagha to pretend to be his lawyer and phone him. Bagha informs Jetha that he needs to drink tea since he has a strong headache. Bagha protests that he should go out because he needs to call Taarak nevertheless when Jetha asks him about his headache and suggests he take a medication to receive some relief. Taarak enters his boss' cabin in the meantime and speaks to him about business, although he is actually waiting for Bagha to call. Can Bagha get out of Gada's shop and reach Taarak? See the show to find out more!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Episode 3803: Boss Ki Permission
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak ultimately chooses to follow Bagha's advice and speak with his supervisor before leaving about his legal issues. While he is at his boss's cabin, Taarak instructs Bagha to pretend to be his lawyer and phone him. Bagha informs Jetha that he needs to drink tea since he has a strong headache. Bagha protests that he should go out because he needs to call Taarak nevertheless when Jetha asks him about his headache and suggests he take a medication to receive some relief. Taarak enters his boss' cabin in the meantime and speaks to him about business, although he is actually waiting for Bagha to call. Can Bagha get out of Gada's shop and reach Taarak? See the show to find out more!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3802 | 20 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3802: Bagha Ka Idea
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak is anxious about the idea to get a day off from work. He contacts Jethalal for assistance in devising an excuse that will easily persuade his supervisor to grant him leave. Taarak dials the Gada Store, but Bagha answers, so Taarak chooses to ask him instead. Bagha is also an employee, thus he must know how to persuade his boss to give him a day off. Bagha hesitates at first, fearing that Taarak will reveal all of this to his boss, Jetha, but Taarak promises him that he will not. Will Bagha's idea be helpful enough for Taarak to get a day off from his work? Stay tuned! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3802, 20 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000225119

snippet.title: Interstellar Time Travel Explained | How Wormholes Work? | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
A wormhole is a theoretical tunnel or shortcut in spacetime that connects two distant regions or even different universes. It is often visualised as a "shortcut" through the fabric of the universe, allowing for faster-than-light travel or a bridge between distant locations. Join Dhruv Rathee on an illuminating journey as he delves into the enigmatic realm of wormholes in this upcoming video. Unveiling the true essence of these cosmic phenomena, Dhruv explores their formation, types, and the tantalising question of whether they could serve as gateways for interstellar travel.

*About* 
------------

Yeh kahani hai ek pyaari si choti bacchi, Avni ki. Avni ke papa, Ashish Mehta hain ek bohot hi mashhur film director lekin woh apni maa, Ayesha Haider ke sath ek chhote aur sadharan ghar mein rehti hai. Ashish ki maa, Dayawanti Mehta hai ek devoted Hindu aur marte dum tak nahi qabool karegi ek Hindu-Muslim ka pyaar. Par Avni issi pyaar ki naajayaz nishani hai. Dayawanti ne tod diya yeh pyaara parivaar aur le aayi apni pasand ki bahu, Neela Parekh. Par dekho kismet ka khel, Neela ke dil ko mili Avni mein khushi aur ban gayi woh uski chahiti. Dayawanti ne koi kasar nahi chhodi barbaad karne mein Ayesha aur uski beti ko. Par Neela ne nahi chhoda Avni ka sath. Avni ne kiya kayi kathinayion ka saamna aur di Dayawanti ko zordaar takkar. Iss mahayudh mein kiski hogi jeet aur kiski hogi haar?

Bagwaan bina mandir ke
Gehrayi bina samundar ke
Tu soch na sakti mere ander ke
Eh lyricsa bina devender ke
In geeta bina devender ke

Di aankh ye meri khol tane
Mane pyaar karya makhol tane
Hove kitna dard khamosi ka
Par khuch na sakta boll tane
Di aankh ye meri khol tane
Mane pyaar karya makhol tane
Hove kitna dard khamosi ka
Par khuch na sakta boll tane
Ban na pave mere bargi tu 
Re kaam dogle kargi tu
Je tere khater main marga 
Ja mere khater margi tu
Ib dikhe jehar mane pani mein
Gani kami mili  meri rani mein
Meri hit pyaar ki kahaani mein 
Kyu galat nibhaya role tane
Di aankh ye meri khol tane
Mane pyaar karya makhol tane
Hove kitna dard khamosi ka
Par khuch na sakta boll tane
Arye di aankh ye meri

Bina paise yaari nibhni na 
Yo fark batave marjanii
Mere pyaar bhare ehsaasa ne 
Va tharak batave marjani
Sala jiste yo mera dil lagya 
Va tarak lagave marjani
Re jo mani mane jannat va 
Mane narak batave marjani
Tere pyaar jehar mere haada mein
Ji kaade swad swada mein
Thi tu gaira ke chakkra mein
Jhajjar aala teri yaada mein
Bande na parkho bane te
Ke pyaar jo mile dingtane te 
Ijjat thi faltu gana te  
Ijjat ke baja diye dhol tane
Di aankh ye meri khol tane
Mane pyaar karya makhol tane
Hove kitna dard khamosi ka
Par kuch na sakta boll tane
Arye di aankh ye meri

Jisi kaal thi usiye aaj se tu
Diya dhokha dhokebaaj se tu 
Kis kis mein yaar ne tovegi 
Mere beete tyme ka raaj se tu
Ja nibhale kiste nibhavegi
Mere barga kade te lyavegi
Ude pyaar ka pave bhora na
Jisma te riste lavegi
Tu ae aakhiri thi tu ae pehla re
Khush rehti yaar ki gaila re
Teri kaali kartoota ne 
Yo chora kar diya maila re
Na piye bina ib kaam chale
Tera naam chale mera jaam chale
Par aaj bhi vohe daam chale 
Lya ib dhikhadu tol tane
Di aankh ye meri khol tane
Mane pyaar karya makhol tane
Hove kitna dard khamosi ka
Par khuch na sakta boll tane
Arye di aankh ye meri

Gaye kade hotha ke payale tere 
Kade aankha ka jaam rehgya
Tu sabki khas bangi main banke aam rehgya 
Ja godi mein sir dharwa ora ke 
Tera yohe to kaam rehgya
Naam banaan chla tha mohbbat ke sehar mein 
Sali mohbbat bik gi
Sala dev badnaam rehgya 
Dev badnaam rehgya

*About* 
------------

Yeh kahani hai ek pyaari si choti bacchi, Avni ki. Avni ke papa, Ashish Mehta hain ek bohot hi mashhur film director lekin woh apni maa, Ayesha Haider ke sath ek chhote aur sadharan ghar mein rehti hai. Ashish ki maa, Dayawanti Mehta hai ek devoted Hindu aur marte dum tak nahi qabool karegi ek Hindu-Muslim ka pyaar. Par Avni issi pyaar ki naajayaz nishani hai. Dayawanti ne tod diya yeh pyaara parivaar aur le aayi apni pasand ki bahu, Neela Parekh. Par dekho kismet ka khel, Neela ke dil ko mili Avni mein khushi aur ban gayi woh uski chahiti. Dayawanti ne koi kasar nahi chhodi barbaad karne mein Ayesha aur uski beti ko. Par Neela ne nahi chhoda Avni ka sath. Avni ne kiya kayi kathinayion ka saamna aur di Dayawanti ko zordaar takkar. Iss mahayudh mein kiski hogi jeet aur kiski hogi haar?

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

-------------------------------------------------
Aageel desires to enter the famed "Red Door," but her companions are terrified of the consequences because anyone who passes through this door dies.
